Package: explicaR
Title: Make R Data Pipelines Interpretable and Visual
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cathal", "Byrne", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cathal470@gmail.com")
Description: Generates interactive visual explanations of multi-script R
    data pipelines. At the macro level, produces a navigable dependency
    graph showing how scripts, functions, and variables relate. At the
    micro level, generates cell-by-cell animated visualisations of
    dplyr/tidyr transformations. Output is a single self-contained HTML
    file shareable without a running server.
